"Here it is."[l][r]
Kanazawa invited me into the hospital room. I could hear faint breathing. A drawn curtain. Beyond it, there she was.[l][r]
...She's supposed to be there, so why is it so quiet?[l][r]
[r]The overwhelming silence made me hesitate to take a step forward.[l][r]
[r]I felt like something immense and heavy would crash down on me if I looked.[r]
...I'm scared.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

