I gulped.[r]
Even so, I looked.[r]
I peered beyond the curtain to see the person lying on the bed.[l][r]
Wavy blonde hair, sky-blue eyes staring intently at the ceiling. There was no mistaking her.[l][r]

[r]"...Yuu?"[l][r]
I softly called out. Yuri lying there just staring at the ceiling reminded me of when she was in the cargo bed of the Kettenkrad.[l][r]
But it's different. Completely different.[l][r]
I called out repeatedly right next to her ear. But she didn't respond at all. It was as if...[l][r]
[cm]...it was as if her soul had left her body.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

