Chito stared at her partner, who was lying on the bed, unable to speak or move.[l][r]
I couldn't tell what kind of expression she had while looking at Yuri from behind.[l][r]
[r]The direct cause of Yuri's coma was supposedly the strong blow to her head when she collapsed.[l][r]
Luckily, her life wasn't in danger. But she doesn't wake up. She should be able to wake up, but it's like she refuses to.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

