[r]There weren’t many pages marked with sticky notes.[l][r]
But my heart felt like it was going to burst.[l][r]

"You know, seeing this might only cause her more pain."[r]
"But, Chito will read it. Once she knows about this notebook, she'll come snatch it with a fierce determination."[r]
"Yeah, you're right."[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

