I closed the notebook and handed it back to Ishii-san.[r]
I took a deep breath and sighed, pressing my hand to my forehead.[l][r]
“I said earlier that I’d want to hurl abuse at a god-like entity responsible for this, but I’d like to amend that.”[l][r]
I clenched my fists tightly. Very tightly. My clenched fists trembled, as if to express my emotions.[l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

